## ✅ Investigation & Cleanup Complete

### Root Cause
**`data-sync-job`** (`owner: test-developer`, `purpose: data synchronization test`) was producing excessive log output (42GB in 6 hours), spilling to `/tmp/sync-buffer-*.log` and driving ephemeral storage on `worker-node-03` to 87%, triggering the `NodeDiskPressure` alert.

### Actions Taken
- **Deleted** `data-sync-job` + its pod `data-sync-job-pod` (cascade: none — no shared resources affected)

